    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Katana Dragon》是一款融合动作冒险与地牢探索的日式RPG。​玩家将扮演忍者“信”与“野比”，踏上破除索根大陆古老诅咒的史诗征程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，你可以学习各式忍术、强化龙之宝石、装备诅咒印记并不断升级；同时要避开陷阱、解开谜题，与强大的敌人激战到底。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开启你的忍者之路，书写属于你的传奇！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索广阔世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/0975bea21891b0783a5b07e14bb27a44.poster.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/0975bea21891b0783a5b07e14bb27a44.webm?t=1772017627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >美丽的索根大地正等待着你的探索。整个地图、隐藏的秘密、各种挑战和地牢均由设计师手工精心打造。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>掌握忍者技能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/b65bfaef47b7f1f4316401a97911be82.poster.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/b65bfaef47b7f1f4316401a97911be82.webm?t=1772017627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断学习全新的忍术，助你解谜、击败敌人，甚至开启通往未知区域的大门，发现深藏的秘密。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与敌人战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/9ac8deb39454f8f5b10cfaf77b8fff60.poster.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/9ac8deb39454f8f5b10cfaf77b8fff60.webm?t=1772017627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与传说中的“五怪”展开激烈战斗——这些强大的生物不仅能喷火、撕咬，甚至能飞行。你能做得完美收集五怪图鉴吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>深入地牢探险</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/27599f53194885a8c055b8855246df42.poster.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/27599f53194885a8c055b8855246df42.webm?t=1772017627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索充满秘密的地牢、井穴和洞窟，寻找珍贵宝藏，检验你辛苦修炼的成果。穿越每个房间、避开陷阱，与Boss展开史诗级对决。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自定义外观</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/c0259652d30f8602ecf2e379b469d373.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富多样的服装供你选择：从和服、盔甲到帽子、面具、裙装，一应俱全，让你随心定制属于自己的忍者风采。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>装备并强化龙之宝石</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/cd833d1f0cd22aa1d0d4395b015231ed.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用蕴含于龙之宝石中的神秘力量，提升你的各种属性。收集不同形状、套装和稀有度的宝石，自由打造最适合你战斗风格的装备。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>小心诅咒印记</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/efb20a39659b8323cada821b4318ceee.avif?t=1772017627\" width=620 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >诅咒印记虽能带来强大增益，但同时也附带危险。没有牺牲就没有收获，你能否承受其中的代价？</p>",
